  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a legendary treasure hunter, looking for the Stone of Silence, a powerful artifact that got lost in an old temple. There, you will find a series of weird machines full of puzzles to crack to gain your freedom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Odd Machines: Lost Artifacts</strong> is a 3D escape room puzzle game where you must solve complex mechanical puzzles, discover hidden objects, and unveil intriguing mysteries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/7201f8fb9431bfe68c0cd23a8927c19b.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/7201f8fb9431bfe68c0cd23a8927c19b.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a world where cryptic vibes, complex mechanisms, and smooth controls from top escape room games blend to challenge your brain skills. You'll tackle unique puzzle sets on a mysterious, gripping adventure. Every machine is crafted to deliver the ultimate escape and exploration thrill.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/dde9c597762682aa71cebda323f7696b.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/dde9c597762682aa71cebda323f7696b.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a puzzling adventure with an eclectic mix of original Victorian machinery, classic and architectural enigmas</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/4220fc946967eb41bc0cee17f0ecf9ed.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/4220fc946967eb41bc0cee17f0ecf9ed.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/d3b9a8b5ddf532406810918246d2b8a9.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/d3b9a8b5ddf532406810918246d2b8a9.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a mesmerizing world where every move reveals new mysteries and changes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/fb0081fdb57734db4078af943358ec5c.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/fb0081fdb57734db4078af943358ec5c.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/997e4a0f412551886fd22b8512181f11.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/997e4a0f412551886fd22b8512181f11.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you get all 8 pieces of the lost stone, you'll be transported into a mystical scene where you'll have to crack numeric puzzles to put the pieces together and finally escape the temple</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/78d07d5f62976ef28c5429cac6fb22d3.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/78d07d5f62976ef28c5429cac6fb22d3.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/12cb76f7d5d47df49b8ae369dd90efa5.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/12cb76f7d5d47df49b8ae369dd90efa5.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sound effects and tunes are so mind-blowingly good that will whisk you away on an unforgettable, vibe-filled adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/23146c8f49082d12db995b8cd1372d05.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/23146c8f49082d12db995b8cd1372d05.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2021 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a legendary treasure hunter, looking for the Stone of Silence, a powerful artifact that got lost in an old temple. There, you will find a series of weird machines full of puzzles to crack to gain your freedom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Odd Machines: Lost Artifacts</strong> is a 3D escape room puzzle game where you must solve complex mechanical puzzles, discover hidden objects, and unveil intriguing mysteries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/7201f8fb9431bfe68c0cd23a8927c19b.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/7201f8fb9431bfe68c0cd23a8927c19b.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a world where cryptic vibes, complex mechanisms, and smooth controls from top escape room games blend to challenge your brain skills. You'll tackle unique puzzle sets on a mysterious, gripping adventure. Every machine is crafted to deliver the ultimate escape and exploration thrill.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras/dde9c597762682aa71cebda323f7696b.avif?t=1765354380\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408360/extras_big/dde9c597762682aa71cebda323f7696b.avif?t=1765354380 width=800 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a puzzling adventure with an eclectic mix of original Victorian machinery, classic and architectural enigmas</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s